name: Overeaten
description:
Main purpose in Overeaten is to feed the fat man until time reaches end. Drag this tasty fat burger in fat man's mouth to feed him. But watch out, because fat man will puke piece of eaten food. Try yourself!

The engine used to create this game is of course Unity.

All arts are made by me.

Only asset wchich I downloaded from internet was music Good Fellow by Komiku ( https://www.chosic.com/download-audio/25477/ )

I hope you'll enjoy!
